data.description: Located in the secure gated community of Waterford Lakes in Silverleaf you will find this stunning 3BR/2.5BA townhome. Built in 2023, this smart home offers the perfect blend of modern living and convenience with a state-of-the-art IQ Panel to control everything in your home including the thermostat and front door directly from your phone. As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the inviting open floor plan that maximizes space and natural light. The spacious living area seamlessly connects to the dining room and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with your loved ones. The contemporary kitchen features sleek, brand-new appliances, ample cabinetry, and plenty of counter space, perfect for food preparation. With its thoughtful layout, this kitchen is sure to be the heart of your home. Upstairs, you'll find three comfortable bedrooms, each thoughtfully designed with your comfort in mind. The primary bedroom boasts a private en-suite bathroom with a single vanity and tub/shower combo. The remaining bedrooms share a well-appointed full bathroom, ensuring convenience for family and guests alike. This townhome's 1,502 square feet of living space offers plenty of room to make it your own, whether you're creating a cozy retreat or a stylish modern oasis. Outside, you'll enjoy the benefits of living in a secure gated community, where safety and peace of mind are top priorities. Situated on a corner lot, there’s plenty of green space to play a game of catch or garden. The community amenities include a swimming pool, fitness center, and more, providing you with a resort-like lifestyle right at your doorstep. Located in Silverleaf, there’s an array of shopping, restaurants, and parks close by. Enjoy!
